name: Setsuna - Redo the Healer
description:
Raphtalia Setsuna from the very wholesome anime Rising of the Shield Hero Redo the Healer

For those of you who know this anime, betchya didn't remember her name was Setsuna ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)

Use weight of 0.8 - 1.0

Use Setsuna with additional tags of "wolf girl, animal feet" for accurate results.

This one was very tough to get right and still is a bit flakey in terms of accuracy.

Even though I memed about Redo the Healer, Setsuna's still pretty cute and has a pretty great design.

Please like, comment and share your gens :)

modelVersions.name: Setsuna v2
modelVersions.description:
Did some fine tuning of dimensions and alpha, added a few more images to the dataset and adjusted images for more consistent color.

Same tags as before can be used.

Massively improved accuracy and quality.

For whatever High-res fix can make it do goofy things sometimes so lowering the de-nosier may be necessary.
